-- Citi names Richard D. Parsons Chairman
-- 
-- Wed Jan 21, 2009 4:45pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/01/21/us-citi-parsons-idUSTRE50K6U320090121

 

 (Reuters) - Citigroup Inc on Wednesday named Richard D. Parsons as chairman of the board of directors. Highlights: 

 * Says appointment effective February 23 * Says Parsons succeeds Sir Win Bischoff * Citi says Win Bischoff will not stand for re-election to the board at Citi's next annual meeting and will retire later this year